metadata.name: P.P.Penguin #1
metadata.description: P.P.Penguins is an arctic-born collection of 5000 Pixel Polar Penguins. Our mission is to create incredible pixel IP and a fun collecting experience for our Penguin Fam!!! Collector's have full IP rights to their NFT. Our wish is for you to pass on the aesthetics of our pixel art and amplify it in the true spirit of web3 and CC0.
